---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Reliable Inspections collects, uses, and protects your personal information."
>
  <main class="py-section-md px-page">
    <div class="contained">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="md:col-span-8 md:col-start-3">
          <header class="mb-el-xl">
            <h1 class="text-title-lg font-semibold mb-el-md">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-body-md text-dark-1">Effective date: January 1, 2025</p>
          </header>

          <div
            class="[&_h2]:text-title-sm [&_h2]:font-semibold [&_h2]:text-dark-3 [&_h2]:mb-el-md [&_h2]:mt-el-xl [&_h3]:text-body-lg [&_h3]:font-semibold [&_h3]:text-dark-3 [&_h3]:mb-el-sm [&_h3]:mt-el-lg [&_p]:text-body-md [&_p]:text-dark-1 [&_p]:mb-el-md [&_ul]:list-disc [&_ul]:pl-el-xl [&_ul]:text-body-md [&_ul]:text-dark-1 [&_ul]:mb-el-md [&_li]:mb-el-sm"
          >
            <p>
              Reliable Inspections ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy.
              This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights
              regarding your data.
            </p>

            <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect information you provide directly when you:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Submit a contact or inspection request form</li>
              <li>Email or call us to schedule a service</li>
              <li>Receive and interact with your inspection report</li>
            </ul>
            <p>This information may include your name, email address, phone number, and property address.</p>

            <p>
              We also collect limited technical data automatically when you visit our website,
              including your browser type, pages visited, and time on site. This data is aggregated
              and not linked to any individual.
            </p>

            <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Schedule and perform inspection services</li>
              <li>Deliver your inspection report and follow-up materials</li>
              <li>Respond to inquiries and provide customer support</li>
              <li>Send service confirmations and appointment reminders</li>
              <li>Improve our website and services</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties.</p>

            <h2>Data Retention</h2>
            <p>
              We retain your personal information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes
              described in this policy, or as required by applicable law. Inspection records are
              typically retained for a minimum of five years.
            </p>

            <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p>
              We may use trusted third-party services to help us operate our business, such as
              email delivery providers. These partners are contractually obligated to keep your
              information confidential and may only use it to perform services on our behalf.
            </p>

            <h2>Cookies and Analytics</h2>
            <p>
              Our website uses privacy-respecting analytics to understand how visitors use our site.
              We do not use advertising cookies or cross-site tracking.
            </p>

            <h2>Your Rights</h2>
            <p>You have the right to:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Request access to the personal data we hold about you</li>
              <li>Ask us to correct inaccurate information</li>
              <li>Request deletion of your data, subject to legal obligations</li>
              <li>Opt out of any marketing communications at any time</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>
              If you have questions about this policy or wish to exercise your rights, please
              contact us at{' '}
              <a
                href="mailto:hello@reliableinspectionsky.com"
                class="text-green-1 underline underline-offset-2"
              >
                hello@reliableinspectionsky.com
              </a>.
            </p>

            <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>
              We may update this policy from time to time. When we do, we will revise the effective
              date at the top of this page. Continued use of our website after any changes
              constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
